Manterror/Injector/Bumblebee:


After the People's Group had retreated, Injector and Bumblebee hading back 
towards their quarters.

"Haha!  Pathetic worthless traitorous Maximal dogs!" Manterror chuckled.  
Turning, out of the corner of an optic view, he turned seeing Dark Mouse.  
"Hmmm..." he pondered.  "WHO ARE YOU!" he yelled to Dark Mouse.

At hearing this, Injector told Bumblebee to just go on ahead, himself heading 
back to where Manterror was.
